                                        smssend.SendWhitelabelEmailAll(RetailerEmail, "Cash Paid Rs." + balance + " to " + dealername + ". New Balance is " + remainretailer + ". Your O/s Credit is " + diff1 + "", "Fund Transfer", adminemail, userid);
                                    }
                                    if (statusSendMailDlmToRetailerFundTransferDlm == "Y")
                                    {
                                        smssend.SendWhitelabelEmailAll(DealerEmail, "Cash Recived Rs." + balance + " From " + retailername + ",his O/s Credit is " + diff1 + "", "Fund Transfer", adminemail, userid);
                                    }
                                    TempData["result"] = ch;
                                }
                            }

                            return Json(ch, JsonRequestBehavior.AllowGet);
                        }
                        else
                        {
                            return Json("Your Previous Request IN Process Please Try After SomeTime", JsonRequestBehavior.AllowGet);
                        }
                    }
                }
                else
                {
                    ViewData["MSG"] = "Transaction Password is Wrong.";
                    ch = "Transaction Password is Wrong.";
                    //  return View();
                    return Json(ch, JsonRequestBehavior.AllowGet);
                }
            }
            catch (Exception ex)
            {
                return Json(ex.Message, JsonRequestBehavior.AllowGet);
            }

            //return Json(ch, JsonRequestBehavior.AllowGet);
        }
        public ActionResult ChkSecurityPassRetailertoRetailer_bal(string txtcode, string hdSuperstokistID, string hdMDDLM, string hdMDComments, string hdPaymentAmount)
        {
            try
            {
                var ch = "";
                var whitelabelid = User.Identity.GetUserId();
                var AdminMail = db.WhiteLabel_userList.SingleOrDefault(s => s.WhiteLabelID == whitelabelid).EmailId;

                var userid = db.Whitelabel_Retailer_Details.FirstOrDefault(a => a.RetailerId == hdSuperstokistID && a.Whitelabelid == whitelabelid).RetailerId;
                string useremail = db.Whitelabel_Retailer_Details.Where(p => p.RetailerId == hdSuperstokistID && p.Whitelabelid == whitelabelid).FirstOrDefault().Email;
                //  string reatilerto = "";
                // var chkmb = db.Retailer_Details.Where(a => a.Mobile == FromRetailerId || a.Email == FromRetailerId).Any();
                //if (chkmb == false)
                //{
                //    TempData["error"] = "This User Not Exist";
                //    return RedirectToAction("Retailer_to_retailer");
                //}
                var reatilerto = db.Whitelabel_Retailer_Details.Where(p => p.RetailerId == hdMDDLM && p.Whitelabelid == whitelabelid).FirstOrDefault().RetailerId;
                var retaileremaillid = db.Whitelabel_Retailer_Details.Where(p => p.RetailerId == hdMDDLM && p.Whitelabelid == whitelabelid).FirstOrDefault().Email;
                //if (remid.Count > 0)
                //{
                //    reatilerto = remid.Single().RetailerId;
                //    retaileremaillid = remid.Single().Email;
                //}
                //else
                //{
                //    reatilerto = db.Retailer_Details.Where(a => a.Email == RetailerId).SingleOrDefault().RetailerId;
                //    retaileremaillid = RetailerId;
                //}
                var password = Encrypt(txtcode);
                var tranpass = (from paa in db.Whitelabel_Trans_HighSecu_Pass where paa.transpass == password && paa.WhitelabelId == whitelabelid select paa).Count();

                if (tranpass > 0)
                {
                    var counts = db.spWhitelabel_FundTransfercount(whitelabelid, userid, reatilerto, "", Convert.ToDecimal(hdPaymentAmount), "Remtorem").SingleOrDefault().msg;
                    int msgcount = Convert.ToInt32(counts);
                    if (msgcount == 0)
                    {
                        msgcount = 60001;
                    }
                    int max_limit = 60000;
                    if (msgcount > max_limit)
                    {
                        System.Data.Entity.Core.Objects.ObjectParameter output = new
                System.Data.Entity.Core.Objects.ObjectParameter("output", typeof(string));
                        ch = db.spWhitelabel_rem_to_rem_bal_transfer_ByAdmin(userid, reatilerto, Convert.ToDecimal(hdPaymentAmount), hdMDComments, "", output).SingleOrDefault().msg.ToString();
                        var remainbal = db.Whitelabel_Remain_reteller_balance.Where(r => r.RetellerId == userid && r.whitelabelid == whitelabelid).Single().Remainamount;
                        var remainbalretailer = db.Whitelabel_Remain_reteller_balance.Where(r => r.RetellerId == reatilerto && r.whitelabelid == whitelabelid).Single().Remainamount;
                        var statusRetailer = db.PushNotificationStatus.Where(a => a.UserRole == "Admin").SingleOrDefault().Status;

                        var statusSendSmsREMToREMFundTransfer = db.Whitelabel_SMSSendAll.Where(a => a.ServiceName == "RemtoRemRemFundTrans" && a.Whitelabelid == whitelabelid).SingleOrDefault().Status;
                        var statusSendMailREMToREMFundTransfer = db.Whitelabel_EmailSendAll.Where(a => a.ServiceName == "RemtoRemRemFundTrans1" && a.Whitelabelid == whitelabelid).SingleOrDefault().Status;

                        var RetailerDetails = db.Whitelabel_Retailer_Details.Where(p => p.RetailerId == userid && p.Whitelabelid == whitelabelid).Single();
                        var statusSendSmsREMToREMFundTransferRetailer = db.Whitelabel_SMSSendAll.Where(a => a.ServiceName == "RemtoRem1RemFundTrans" && a.Whitelabelid == whitelabelid).SingleOrDefault().Status;
                        var statusSendMailREMToREMFundTransferRetailer = db.Whitelabel_EmailSendAll.Where(a => a.ServiceName == "RemtoRem1RemFundTrans1" && a.Whitelabelid == whitelabelid).SingleOrDefault().Status;

                        var RetailerMobileRetailerDetails = db.Whitelabel_Retailer_Details.Where(p => p.RetailerId == reatilerto && p.Whitelabelid == whitelabelid).Single();

                        if (ch == "Balance Transfer SuccessFully.")
                        {
                            smssend.sms_init_whitelabel(whitelabelid, statusSendSmsREMToREMFundTransferRetailer, "N", "FUNDTRANSFERBALANCETRANSFER", RetailerMobileRetailerDetails.Mobile, hdPaymentAmount, useremail, remainbalretailer);

                            smssend.sms_init_whitelabel(whitelabelid, statusSendSmsREMToREMFundTransfer, "N", "BALANCETRANSFERRETAILER", RetailerDetails.Mobile, retaileremaillid, hdPaymentAmount, remainbal);

                            if (statusSendMailREMToREMFundTransferRetailer == "Y")
                            {
                                smssend.SendWhitelabelEmailAll(RetailerMobileRetailerDetails.Email, "Balance " + Convert.ToDecimal(hdPaymentAmount) + " Transfer to " + useremail + " is Successfully Transfer. Remain Balance is " + remainbalretailer + "", "Fund Transfer", AdminMail, whitelabelid);
                            }
                            if (statusSendMailREMToREMFundTransfer == "Y")
                            {
                                smssend.SendWhitelabelEmailAll(RetailerDetails.Email, "Balance Transfer Successfully To Retailer Id is " + retaileremaillid + " and Balance is " + Convert.ToDecimal(hdPaymentAmount) + ", Remain Balance is " + remainbal + "", "Fund Transfer", AdminMail, whitelabelid);
                            }

                            TempData["success"] = ch;
                            return Json(ch, JsonRequestBehavior.AllowGet);
                        }
                        else
                        {

                            TempData["error"] = ch;
                            return Json(ch, JsonRequestBehavior.AllowGet);
                        }
                    }
                    else
                    {
                        return Json("Your Previous Request IN Process Please Try After SomeTime", JsonRequestBehavior.AllowGet);
                    }

                }
                else
                {
                    ViewData["MSG"] = "Transaction Password is Wrong.";
                    ch = "Transaction Password is Wrong.";
                    //  return View();
                    return Json(ch, JsonRequestBehavior.AllowGet);
                }
            }
            catch (Exception ex)
            {
                return Json(ex.Message, JsonRequestBehavior.AllowGet);
            }
        }

